  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK869">
<l>ceṟuvārkkuc cēṇikavā viṉpa maṟivilā</l>
<l>vañcum pakaivarp peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There will be no end of lofty delights to the victorious, if their foes are (both) ignorant and timid.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
